# Backend Design: AI-Powered Appraisal System (Django)

## Framework Choice

| Decision | Selection | Justification |
|----------|-----------|----------------|
| **Framework** | Django 5.0+ | Batteries-included, robust ORM, built-in admin, excellent security |
| **DRF** | Django REST Framework 3.14+ | REST API development, serializers, authentication |
| **Runtime** | Python 3.11+ | Latest stable, improved performance |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 16+ | Primary database |
| **ORM** | Django ORM | Built-in, powerful, migration system |
| **Job Queue** | Celery + Redis | Distributed task queue |
| **GitHub Client** | PyGithub + requests | Official GitHub API integration |
| **Webhook Handler** | Django views + HMAC | Secure webhook processing |
| **Testing** | pytest-django | Unit and integration tests |

