### Layer Responsibility Matrix

| Layer | Responsibility | What NOT to do |
|-------|----------------|----------------|
| **View** | Handle HTTP, validation, permissions | No DB queries, no business logic |
| **Service** | Business logic, orchestration, transactions | No HTTP concerns, no direct model access |
| **Repository** | Data access, ORM queries, caching | No business rules |
| **Model** | Define data structure, relationships | No complex business logic |
| **Serializer** | Validate input, format output | No DB queries |

